import React from "react" import SearchBar from "./../components/SearchBar" import SongCard from "./../components/SongCard" import { drawSongsSection } from "./../" let alphabet = [ "#", "A", "B", "C", "D", "E", "F", "G", "H", "I", "J", "K", "L", "M", "N", "Ñ", "O", "P", "Q", "R", "S", "T", "U", "V", "W", "X", "Y", "Z" ] function drawAlphabet() { return alphabet.map((letter) => {letter}) } export default function Songs(props) { let { SongsList } = props return (
{drawSongsSection(Object.values(SongsList))}
{drawAlphabet()}
) }
